

## Interactive graphs

import matplotlib
matplotlib.use('TkAgg')  # or 'Qt5Agg' if you have PyQt5

```
pip install tk        # for TkAgg
# or
pip install PyQt5     # for Qt5Agg
```

Stack
```
matplotlib (your plot code)
     ↓
Backend (TkAgg / Qt5Agg)  ← tells matplotlib HOW to draw a window
     ↓
Toolkit (Tk / PyQt5)       ← the actual GUI library that opens the OS window
     ↓
Your screen
```
